Python Bindings for libkondo4
---------------------------

This directory is an example of how to use swig to create a Python wrapper
for libkondo4.


To Build and Test:
------------------

1. Edit the Makefile to set the proper paths for Python.h and swig.

2. Build the kondo library (libkondo.so) in the parent directory:
   make -C ../

3. Build Native Wrapper Library (_pykondo.so)
   make

4. Test an example:
   ./run_motion.py
